Are we supposed to know each other?

6
00:01:11,838 --> 00:01:15,710
Definitely. I mean, we're supposed to.
We don't, but we should.

7
00:01:17,516 --> 00:01:21,216
- Ray. Ray Koval.
- Theresa Corrado.

8
