If I was drunk, I'd be coming on to you.

14
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,424
That's a relief.

15
00:01:44,537 --> 00:01:47,598
If I was drunk,
I'd be saying how amazing you look

16
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:50,236
and how crazy it is
that you're standing here on your own.

17
00:01:50,313 --> 00:01:53,479
