Pam, Pam, easy, don't tear it.
Pam, Pam, Pam, Pam, just... Careful.

167
00:17:05,665 --> 00:17:07,259
- For Christ's sake, Duke, keep your shirt on.
- Just...

168
00:17:07,368 --> 00:17:10,603
Do something useful.
Punch up Tully's fingerprints.

169
00:17:11,477 --> 00:17:13,605
Wow. Look at this.

170
00:17:14,583 --> 00:17:16,450
So is this the big one?

171
00:17:19,492 --> 00:17:22,259
- I gotta call Garsik right away.
Yeah.

172
00:17:23,133 --> 00:17:25,969
Come on.
I need a secure line at Equikrom.

173
00:17:45,978 --> 00:17:48,311
- How are you?
- Good. How are you?

174
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:05,212
<i>CLAIRE: Houston.</i>
<i>This was over the weekend.</i>

175
