186
00:18:40,817 --> 00:18:42,309
Why does this guy look familiar?

187
00:18:42,422 --> 00:18:46,259
He had a briefcase
full of sales projections stolen last year.

188
00:18:46,663 --> 00:18:49,759
- Is this the guy who bought the boat?
- Same guy.

189
00:18:50,302 --> 00:18:54,073
- All right. Get a team up his ass tonight.
- I sent them this morning.

190
00:18:56,281 --> 00:18:57,978
We're in a meeting.

191
00:18:59,255 --> 00:19:01,817
Now? Everyone?

192
00:19:04,029 --> 00:19:05,932
Well, did they say why?

193
00:19:10,174 --> 00:19:13,010
It's Tully. Mr. Tully's coming down.

194
00:19:13,115 --> 00:19:16,348
He wants the entire floor gathered
in five minutes.

195
00:19:51,221 --> 00:19:54,217
<i>AIDE: Dick, it's just that you have</i>
<i>a very busy schedule today.</i>

