207
00:20:24,953 --> 00:20:27,448
All right, let's have a look at me.

208
00:20:32,636 --> 00:20:34,105
There should be another vehicle.

209
00:20:34,173 --> 00:20:36,108
Yeah. Change of plans.
You're going with them.

210
00:20:36,176 --> 00:20:40,378
Everybody's going. Let's go, come on.
Get out there and sell it, folks!

211
00:20:40,484 --> 00:20:43,480
Go, go, go! Come on!
Get the hell out of here!

212
00:20:51,005 --> 00:20:54,171
