Leave it running. I'm driving.

213
00:21:06,568 --> 00:21:07,866
This is starting to look pretty good.

214
00:21:07,938 --> 00:21:10,339
I can't even tell them apart.
Which one is the new one?

215
00:21:10,410 --> 00:21:11,741
Right here.

216
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:14,743
- This is 16.
- That's a match.

217
00:21:17,589 --> 00:21:19,287
Boris, handwriting?

218
00:21:20,762 --> 00:21:23,633
Hundred percent. It's Howard Tully.

219
00:21:23,736 --> 00:21:26,708
All right.
Burkett & Randle, here we come!

220
00:21:26,775 --> 00:21:27,867
Guys?

221
00:21:30,715 --> 00:21:33,882
Duke? I'm locked out. Again.

222
00:21:35,592 --> 00:21:38,028
Yeah, I'm standing right outside.

223
00:21:38,798 --> 00:21:42,431
Of course it's me!
Who the hell else has this number?

