to work with he can forget it.

962
01:14:40,475 --> 01:14:42,911
You're gonna get that job.

963
01:14:42,979 --> 01:14:44,743
Without knowing what the product is?

964
01:14:44,815 --> 01:14:47,149
Well, that's the point. Nobody knows.

965
01:14:47,253 --> 01:14:49,121
All we have to do is get there first.

966
01:14:49,225 --> 01:14:52,390
You on one side, me on the other.
It's perfect.

967
01:14:53,300 --> 01:14:56,136
What does all this have to do
with Nigel Bingham?

968
01:14:56,238 --> 01:14:58,835
He's Duke's drinking buddy.
They play cards twice a week.

969
01:14:58,943 --> 01:14:59,967
You call Nigel.

970
