What is that?

987
01:15:47,905 --> 01:15:50,569
It's a thong. It was in your closet.

988
01:15:53,382 --> 01:15:55,216
That's not possible.

989
01:15:55,621 --> 01:15:57,591
Well, whose are they?

990
01:15:58,393 --> 01:16:01,957
- Nobody's because it's impossible.
- Impossible what?

991
01:16:02,368 --> 01:16:06,363
That someone would leave them,
or you'd forget or that I'd find them?

992
01:16:06,443 --> 01:16:09,380
Impossible because I've been faithful.
Which closet?

993
01:16:09,448 --> 01:16:11,975
- Which closet?
- This is insane.

994
01:16:12,086 --> 01:16:14,386
- You're denying this?
- Absolutely.

995
01:16:14,457 --> 01:16:17,122
The only woman who's been in this place
since I moved in is the landlady

996
01:16:17,229 --> 01:16:19,256
and she couldn't wear that as a wristband.

997
01:16:19,333 --> 01:16:21,235
So where did they come from?

998
01:16:21,305 --> 01:16:24,104
Look, I swear to you.

999
01:16:24,176 --> 01:16:26,646
Claire, I swear,
I swear on all things good and true,

1000
01:16:26,747 --> 01:16:29,583
I have no idea who they belong to.
And the fact that you don't believe me,

1001
01:16:29,654 --> 01:16:31,953
the fact that we've been through
everything that we've been through

1002
01:16:32,024 --> 01:16:36,625
and that you still don't trust me on this,
is, quite frankly, disturbing.

1003
01:16:37,469 --> 01:16:40,372
Well, in that case, I'll put them back on.

1004
01:16:41,042 --> 01:16:42,601
They're yours?

1005
01:16:42,679 --> 01:16:44,376
You passed.

1006
01:16:44,483 --> 01:16:46,179
You're gaming me?

1007
01:16:46,286 --> 01:16:48,779
I just needed to hear you say it.

1008
01:16:52,532 --> 01:16:55,230
- You're that upset?
- Yeah, I think so.

1009
01:17:03,520 --> 01:17:06,012
But kind of turned on, too, right?

1010
01:17:08,095 --> 01:17:12,900
The drag is I've only got 55 minutes
to make it up to you.

1011
01:17:54,987 --> 01:17:56,421
Forget it.

1012
01:17:59,261 --> 01:18:01,163
I never liked this game.

1013
01:18:01,265 --> 01:18:05,797
Any sport that puts a limit on your score
is a complete waste of time.

1014
01:18:06,676 --> 01:18:08,805
Three hundred, that's it?

1015
01:18:08,881 --> 01:18:12,844
What, are you gonna bust your nut to do
something 9 million other jokers might do?

1016
01:18:12,954 --> 01:18:14,720
Stupidest damn thing I ever heard of.

1017
